0010 REM "MPR - Production Forecast Worksheet (Input Overlay)"
0020 REM "Program MPR.CA"
0022 REM "+-----------------------------------------------------------+"
0024 REM "| ADD+ON Software, Inc. Advantage/V Version 6.0.0 - 15May96 |"
